OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fabout Bradley every day'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Former England striker Jermain Defoe   
OL,6, has said he thinks about Bradley Lowery
OL,7, every day.                             
OL,9,FDefoe became "best mates" with the     
OL,10,Fyoung Sunderland fan, who was diagnosed
OL,11,Fwith neuroblastoma - a rare type of    
OL,12,Fcancer - when he was 18 months old.    
OL,14,FBradley passed away in 2017 aged six,  
OL,15,Fwith his story touching the hearts of  
OL,16,Fthousands.                             
OL,18,FReflecting on the friendship on BBC    
OL,19,Fpodcast Jermain Defoe: Outside The Box,
OL,20,Fhe described it as "a special time".   
